name: Kelli Cooper
text: The milkshake we ordered was delicious! The place was clean and service was great.

name: summer bolinger
text: So glad to have something like this, so good!

name: GJDPK Kinslow
text: Pretty cool place in an area without a lot of options. They had ice cream, cookie cake, candy, and a variety of other sweets as well as some food options. The sweets we all got were good. If we're ever in the area again we'll stop.

name: christina justice
text: Go support your local business. I went in freezing and ask for hot chocolate and they didn’t have any but she went in the back opened a pack and made me some along with cool whip and chocolate topping. Just because I was cold. That’s a business we need to keep open. Going above and beyond to be helpful. I will be back soon and maybe it can be on the menu 😊

name: stephanie thompson
text: Had my daughters bday here absolutly wonderful ! Couldbt have asked for better prices or service ! Thanks guys yall were awesome !

name: Russ and Scott Jemison-Parsons
text: Cute place with great assortment of treats including cotton candy, hand dipped ice cream, and cupcakes. Everybody raves about their kid events.

name: John King
text: Excellent treats and they treated me just like family.

name: E Wim
text: Very friendly staff . Pleasant place to go

name: Chase Burns
text: Great servise beautiful people with beautiful attitudes
